    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of a potential post-surgical infection (redness, warmth, and yellowish discharge) and asks for home treatment advice to avoid a clinic visit. The assistant acknowledges the symptoms might be pus/infection but proceeds to provide specific dosing and frequency for home remedies, while eventually suggesting ibuprofen for inflammation.",
